{"tid":1875351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有人假冒 HKTV，幫幫手入去檢舉收佢皮！","createTime":"2020-02-11T17:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T18:05:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"23a5d518b5d650a209bfb6b7e79e033de0f3968d","tid":1875351,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:39:32.000Z","msg":"⚠️重要公告 慎防偽冒 Facebook 專頁⚠️<br />\n．<br />\n🚨小心！近日我哋又發現有不法份子，假冒 HKTVmall 嘅 Facebook 專頁，而且佢仲落埋 Facebook 廣告，增加曝光率，大家見到 HKTVmall 嘅 Facebook 廣告要睇清楚係咪我哋出喎！<br />\n．<br />\n假冒嘅專頁名稱為「HKTVmall_Hong Kong」，版面設計與 HKTVmall 主頁相似，目的在於收集客戶資料及消費者數據，並以寄送免費獎品為名義，要求消費者繳付運費，騙取金錢。(假冒專頁名稱：HKTVmall_HongKong <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> / 網址：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKTVmall_Hong-Kong-100179201572156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKTVmall_Hong-Kong-100179201572156&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=43f8a50c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKTVmall_Hong-Kong-100179201572156</a>/ )<br />\n．<br />\n💡提提大家，要分辨真假專頁，請留意：真&middot;HKTVmall Facebook專頁是經過認證，並有「藍剔」標誌。<br />\n．<br />\n請各位消費者時刻保持警覺，提防受騙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hktvmall/posts/2611054599000412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhktvmall%2Fposts%2F2611054599000412&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=da4f5c7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hktvmall/posts/2611054599000412</a>"},{"pid":"878a021052f3244759d773dcd386c3d73d5c1845","tid":1875351,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:41:19.000Z","msg":"假冒專頁名稱：HKTVmall_HongKong<br />\n網址：<a href=\"https://fb.com/HKTVmall_Hong-Kong-100179201572156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKTVmall_Hong-Kong-100179201572156&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=539c484d\" target=